        "body":  "Codex re-review: APPROVED (content)\n\nI re-checked `cdc4879` after the round-4 fix. The last live alias-over-`Handoff` listing in `crates/editor-state/src/lib.rs:44-45` now includes `MenuStateHandoff`, and the previous handoff/snapshot set-listing findings are resolved.\n\nReviewed the broad source-doc surface again:\n- Live handoff listings now include `MenuStateHandoff` where they are set/listing prose.\n- Live snapshot-aggregator listings now include `MenuStateSnapshot`.\n- Remaining omissions are correctly historical Rule-of-Three / dated changelog prose or individual field/type docs, not current set listings.\n- Functional design remains sound: `PlayState` is the validity authority, `MenuStateSnapshot` is observational, and the host only routes booleans.\n\nCI is fully green at `cdc4879` (13/13, MERGEABLE/CLEAN), `git diff --check` is clean, and there are no Cargo/edge changes.\n\nNon-blocking note: the PR body still has an old scope line (`9 files`, `+254/-4`) while the live diff is now 10 files, `+378/-34` after correction rounds. I do not consider that a content blocker for the source changes.\r\n",
